PrecisRegulations Amending the WILD ANIMAL AND PLANT TRADE REGULATIONS which exempt pets as well as personal and household effects from the permit requirements of the Convention on International Trade in Endangered Species of Wild Fauna and Flora, allow prosecutions to be based on what an item is represented to be, specify the kind of information to be set out in a Removal Notice, and extend the period preceding forfeiture, effective January 15, 2000.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2000-0003 Publication Date: 2000-01-05

precis:
Regulations Amending the WILD ANIMAL AND PLANT TRADE REGULATIONS which
exempt pets as well as personal and household effects from the permit
requirements of the Convention on International Trade in Endangered Species
of Wild Fauna and Flora, allow prosecutions to be based on what an item is
represented to be, specify the kind of information to be set out in a
Removal Notice, and extend the period preceding forfeiture, effective
January 15, 2000.
